    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2009-03-05</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2009-03-25T15:31:18Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>COLA Fairness Act of 2009 - Requires the Bureau of Labor Statistics of the Department of Labor to establish: (1) a mapping of the United States comprising 14 specified regions; and (2) particular monthly consumer price indices for such regions for computation of cost-of-living increases for Social Security and Medicare (title XVIII of the Social Security Act) benefits.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>COLA Fairness Act of 2009</title>
